column5: Lot of fish for a buddy and I today. A few decent ones but no derby fish. One nice hog weighing in at 27 pounds.
Wow nice slabs of fish.  How much did the last one weigh?
27 pounds. we also had 2 others that were 25 pounds. Hope Tundra and lighting and I can get some like that on Saturday in the tourney were in.
Right on man  Those are some slabs for sure.  Where did you head out from?  Joey
Nice fish!! That would be a fun day fer sure!!  Sinker
Nice fish iceguy there seems to be some nice big fish out there this year  Rob
KEEP ON DREAMING MIKEY >>>>>>YOU KNOW THE BOATS ARE ALWAYS OPEN YOU JUST NEED TO DRIVE
Lake O sure has some huge Salmon! Thanks for sharing and good luck on the weekend!
Nice work Rob!!!  Let's put some hogs in the boat this weekend!  :-)
Good going guys!!  good luck this weekend!!
We launch out of ashbridges. Smelly launch but good fishing on the drop off. near the Island.
that little baby salmon is cool looking. like a stuffed toy or something. not like i like stuffed toys or anything. i hate them actually, they remind me of creepy garage sales.
